culated as 100 - 50 x logMAR</td></tr><tr><td><a href="CodeSystem-custom-codes-to-be-submitted-to-SNOMED-or-LOINC.html#custom-codes-to-be-submitted-to-SNOMED-or-LOINC-Numberofrecognizedoptotypes">Number of recognized optotypes</a></td><td>Number of recognized optotypes</td><td/></tr></table></li></ul></div>
